<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20200818/731f7e8604f84cbf9d7f7430c8033038.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/images01/20200818/f20ac389ab7b4d1080b76e166036eb3b.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>……</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>『凤园椰珍』开新店啦！</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>...</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>每个广州人都逃不掉的“椰子鸡一哥”</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>火了7年，开哪，哪里就排队</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>2W+条好评，稳居大众TOP①</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>3只"混血”椰子煮1只鸡</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>汤底比阿妈煲的汤还甜</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">/在法律范围内，以上活动解释权归商家所有/</p>            <div class="lookall-box">
