<p class="ql-align-justify">而且一整杯都是料</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">///</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">装修环境成功燃起青春回忆</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">带你一秒穿越回80年代！</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">一起喝跨它~</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">正佳广场旁·天河南一路店</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">YOUTAO</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">有·桃·饮·料·厂</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>/在法律范围内，活动解释权归商家所有/</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20200818/1062fdaa166b420c8723e351cfc3a3b9.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>复古年代感十足，进驻广州CBD</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>▩ 人气超高！排队是标配 ▩</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20200818/b85ab08f38a2477d9f262e1aa0927971.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">凭借着<strong>网红复古风</strong>的造型，刷爆了各大平台！排队3小时也要打卡的网红奶茶店，<strong>终于来广州啦，就在正佳广场旁！</strong>想喝记得要趁早来...</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>▩ 杯杯都是真材实料 ▩</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20200818/b6bcc1f9810c4d16bfcd0b20eb62dcf4.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">不难看出，有桃主打性价比。每一杯都是真材实料，优质红茶和纯牛奶打造。招牌也是<strong>“纯奶制造，实惠多料”</strong>，而且<strong>“好喝不贵”</strong>，瞬间被圈粉了~</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>▩ 喝到就是赚到 ▩</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20200818/b3484ba08ece495fa68af3f36df02bbc.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">●●●</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">夏日必喝的快乐水！五大系列任选，仙草/珍珠/芋圆/红豆通通都有，喝两口就回本~</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/images01/20200818/7d2a69f4e0824c58b1f5dba4ac2257ef.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>几乎人手一杯的经典出品</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>▩ 豆/乳/大/满/贯 ▩</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>YOUTAO</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20200818/741c16164d0b4c4ca627e43f4c769688.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>- 豆乳大满贯 -</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">Douru Grand slam</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">选择困难症患者必pick！在经典奶茶底再加入<strong>秘制豆花、手工芋圆</strong>，最后在新鲜淡奶油雪顶上撒满<strong>醇香黄豆粉</strong>，豆乳爱好者的人生大满贯出杯！</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>“半碗秘制豆花打底”</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20200818/180d979c061145448b92d19d69162fe2.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20200818/3536c4fdd4b5406daf65a995e5bc1804.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/images01/20200818/dbb6f7c3b2b34bac86f54e57cb08e5d5.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20200818/d78692c969a6420588d3f0e6ea74647d.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">一把黄莹莹的豆子，经过一番风云便成为了雪白的豆花，<strong>豆香奶味饱满又香甜！</strong>口感十分像布丁，是真的很嫩滑，在勺子上颤巍巍~像极一个白胖子！</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>“用料超良心，满嘴香甜滑嫩”</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/images01/20200818/31069246c29e4acf8e3b59b9bd644b0a.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">奶茶底和豆花的混搭，产生不一样的反应，舌尖感觉“滑嫩”到极致！像吃布丁一般，<strong>完全不用舌头发力，绵绵熘熘地就进了肚~</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>“甜蜜奶油雪顶，一口就沦陷！”</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>豆乳浓郁醇厚，雪顶顺滑如丝，</strong>当这份甜蜜缠绕在舌尖，像极了初恋时的美好。吃一口，回味无限，吃两口，快乐加倍！</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>▩ 嫩/仙/草/大/满/贯 ▩</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>YOUTAO</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20200818/6464cbba71d943ac9b6187fbc941ab7e.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>- 嫩仙草大满贯 -</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">Shao xian cao Grand slam</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>有桃饮料厂的招牌就是这一杯『豆乳奶茶』了</strong>，满满一大杯的豆乳奶茶，从颜值上就俘获了大家的心。</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>“鲜制豆乳奶茶，肚子里都是料”</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>1// 加入Q弹爽滑烧仙草</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20200818/272d93cdafda430b8bf054abc90c7fcf.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>2// 红豆、芋圆、花生碎统统不能少</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20200818/c0abde63f9834408983b5021c265af93.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>3// 最后加入调制好的奶茶，就完成啦~</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20200818/c9be894aad484d059495ecbe0c11a337.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>烧仙草、红豆、芋圆、碎花生...满满的料！</strong>这一碗细腻冰凉的大满贯，一口滑熘下去，入口满足又充实，简直就是从视觉到味觉的享受!</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20200818/ae53cfa13be34e1fae778eac9b438d2f.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/images01/20200818/8f06620e17e3420593b220530e93563d.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20200818/0083dd75f7144c88a08688c84521beb0.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20200818/d88f948eb0cd472982f53aa4c37a180f.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>每一种小料本身的味道与奶茶碰撞在一起</strong>，香甜绵密、层次更为丰富，每一口都是料，边喝边嚼让人停不下来！</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>“满足感MAX！”</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20200818/1fcab246dbd345f7ad9c2b69d4df4426.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20200818/5272a2e6e515476b88b9dae5a47878ad.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">● ● ●</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20200818/5fe5501257434534b7d4e8a10874c30b.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>鲜奶的香醇和烧仙草的滑嫩完美融合，</strong>也太快乐了吧！火热的天气来一杯，让你像是在38°C的天气里游泳，<strong>一口就治愈夏天的燥热</strong>~</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20200818/bc111e745df64a7f829c301c98070221.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>这几款也尽管点，踩雷算我输</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>▩ 雪/糕/嫩/仙/草/双/拼 ▩</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20200818/f14c2203cca149bea9e7103c533c739d.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>绵密冰淇淋搭配Q弹烧仙草，每一口都带着满满的冰爽气息</strong>。喝一口，那独特的味道在口中蔓延开来，瞬间抓住你的味蕾！</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20200818/0b3c381b90494ffa870dce8d0624f342.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20200818/4806ce7389ff42ff93aae8a26ab3b35a.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20200818/89b98ed0d9b24eb4a90996923507b6f8.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">顶上的雪糕口感非常的顺滑，入口那一层鲜奶的香味会迅速化开蔓延，<strong>咬下去的绵密扎实口感，奶味极其浓厚</strong>~</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20200818/fcc3c08195c64380984cb0ff1d92c478.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20200818/8dc5cfe089fc4885909878649650638b.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">烧仙草和雪糕的混搭，让整杯饮品浓厚香醇。<strong>实实在在的品质用料，喝到的每一口都满满是料，</strong>让人心生愉悦。</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>▩ 热/情/果/翡/翠/冻/冻 ▩</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20200818/0398acc9a49f4ee39214bc781f3613df.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">从颜色看起来就很热情很有夏日感，<strong>一口下去能喝到好多百香果粒</strong>，搭配翡翠在口中绽放<strong>酸酸甜甜</strong>的味道，爱了爱了。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/images01/20200818/bf45f33daf83464c9234b52973a7d377.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">＜＜＜＜＜＜＜＜＜＜＜＜＜＜＜</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20200818/efd4fc0e6f4b469a8cbe09a1587bce40.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">勐吸一口，感受每一颗金黄色的果肉在嘴里散发出的酸爽，<strong>果粒柔软富有弹性，酸甜香浓的滋味在口中弥漫</strong>~</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>▩ 豆/花/芋/圆/双/拼 ▩</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20200818/f5703e134c074d3b89b7aeb928c761cf.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20200818/7ecff0e131bd43d9a41cbefacb6f01ab.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20200818/cd6de6d36f2a4d75a7610ef07051b76d.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>芋圆波波外层软糯，嚼起来韧劲十足</strong>，口感上佳，<strong>搭配嫩嫩的豆花</strong>，形成口感的反差，让人享受到两种不同的美味体验~</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>▩ 这些统统都要安排上 ▩</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/images01/20200818/9470c220a1b346188d3ac996243e637f.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>特调冰咖</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20200818/0c834914f93b45f1a8034c0eede46eb2.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>西柚冻冻</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20200818/2f4df9e0898a4927abd93cba8e5f1df2.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>柠檬翡翠</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">这杯<strong>冰咖</strong>居然还会“分层”，不仅颜值高，味道也很让人惊喜~<strong>西柚冻冻、柠檬翡翠</strong>...清新的茶香混合着水果的香甜，凉爽十足。使劲嘬一口，满满鲜甜清凉！</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20200818/20fa1c0c0687440992016b819c932893.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>童年回忆满满的『奶茶小铺』</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20200818/8a1b7f72e9d64e88ac822a64257fb7a8.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20200818/d53cb255e8204b34b4f8f7d8bc2bd7b9.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20200818/a19d2d0a41cc43c98f76ac7396fc42cc.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20200818/05902c7d2f7b4af1848ebe357b5990ea.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20200818/c0657768d10d49028dbb8bdd9ff275be.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">一进店门，走错片场的错觉依然存在，分分钟穿越到1980年代，『有桃饮料厂』<strong>总是能够把每一个怀旧的细节做到极致。</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20200818/fe9f2a0145c74255a0d85e8f96a75b2e.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20200818/11d697ea180640e5b408e4ef704b7af6.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">摆得整整齐齐的饮料瓶罐、小零食和充满儿时回忆的矮板凳，瞬间将<strong>时间推回那童真无忧的年代</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20200818/8ccca1eb11134d17b4743f7b6b33bf9e.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>/在法律范围内，活动解释权归商家所有/</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20200818/8001e17612234978b38bf0033e2d037b.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>有桃饮料厂（天河南一路店）</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>店铺地址:</strong></p>
