<div class="hidden-content control-hide">
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20200818/9fc153bbb7904d689a1f129c4bc3003f.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>首秀的“小儿子”，猪唛来了！</strong>新式简餐，传统手工制作，将给大家展示独特的味道体验~</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20200818/a6b2cc2bf5594385b9ea9ccd81366a8d.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">▩ 『肉肉猪扒包』，食肉兽挚爱 ▩</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>。招牌脆皮猪扒包，每桌必点</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20200818/5a2e18546e264cf19d49cfb0b7e5e50e.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">这款C位出道的猪扒包，你可别错过了！即点即做，每一只都用料超勐，<strong>松软面包胚+plus版猪扒+农家蔬菜+满满酱料....</strong>份量实在惊人。</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">❶ Baked bread, soft and crisp</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>现烤面包，松软酥脆</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20200818/91ddb46f1346469cb6a66f3c06e22a78.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20200818/21d3015d8b4741e08ef0f5c2bb1ab7a3.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20200818/6e0efabb50f14503a470fb75beb06387.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">每天新鲜拿货的面包，采用<strong>传统的制作手法</strong>，面包的表层需刷一层新鲜黄油，这样面包烤起来格外酥香。</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">❷ Deep-fried, fresh and juicy</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>猪扒现点现炸，鲜嫩多汁</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20200818/c6977f6aa9b84a2c82939c7524fa6304.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20200818/e112cff82cd149dfb013543f9d4aef44.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/images01/20200818/9a7bde149d48454f9c7af7e83d18a641.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">猪扒包中灵魂般存在的猪排，每一块超级大块，腌制后经过高温铁板的油煎，<strong>现点现煎，一吃就知道是新鲜出炉</strong>。</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>比巴掌还大猪扒</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>超大猪扒</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20200818/5c42e026ad5247b0a47c3dbbd8d472f6.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20200818/101c3272043143eb9b856df36c6c5a8b.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>每块猪扒精选猪嵴椎内测的嫩肉，</strong>猪扒带着特调酱汁腌制的香味，香滑而又厚实，食肉兽们冲鸭！</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20200818/5d5be3b9ee5943f2a705c8bc1309e2e0.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">脆口的包底夹着一大块鲜嫩多汁的猪扒，外脆内嫩，<strong>一口下去肉汁都要溢出来了</strong>。</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>加入灵魂秘制酱料</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20200818/51841a345f754c78a6ce14c254149d9a.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/images01/20200818/5e16d06050464aeba66b702a9eb53d3e.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">猪扒包里的配料和酱汁都很足，<strong>带着特调酱汁腌制的香味</strong>，口口爆酱，香滑而又厚实~</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>满口鲜嫩多汁</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20200818/01ef95992ea44871a7e8737faa84e5c5.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20200818/1bb9f200b593447e943afd2764b1ca1c.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20200818/e269bfb60a5742bab141bfc9ef8c89f9.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">切开看看TA的横切面清晰地看到里面的配料<strong>层层分明，分量还很足</strong>，吃起来外脆里嫩，肉汁饱满不油腻！快跟我一起pick它~</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>。人气口味猪扒包，全场任你选</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20200818/eb12704375ed424e8a9069a910532ec7.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">＜＜＜＜＜＜＜＜＜＜＜＜＜＜＜</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20200818/e097a46b527141459a36b82d1b2d1b25.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">让菠萝包控尖叫的<strong>黄金猪扒菠萝包</strong>、有超大一只鸡腿的<strong>黑椒脆皮鸡腿包</strong>...通通都是店内的热门选手哦，各式口味总一款合你心意~</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20200818/49e2ff70044f48ddb6c704598510bbe1.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">▩ 这些都是经典，一起pick ▩</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>。金牌安玛葡塔</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20200818/1f61d1a0d64d4c1ea349a4346e4101a0.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">猪唛家的每个葡塔都有着<strong>精致圆润的挞皮、金黄的蛋液</strong>，还有<strong>焦糖的比例都掌握得刚刚好</strong>~一口下去，满口浓郁的蛋香味。</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">❹ Fresh baked</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>手工葡塔新鲜出炉</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20200818/ac752651f09147e8bfd949e0ff262c68.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">新鲜出炉的葡挞的挞皮简直酥脆的不行，<strong>外酥里嫩的丰富口感和浓郁的蛋奶香味</strong>，让你吃10个也不会腻~</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20200818/289bab7577724dc7a727e600b7951771.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20200818/c24d21024ad446fdb4ce0fff873eadc9.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">猪唛深知焦糖的奥秘，既让焦糖在蛋挞表面留下点点烧焦的外表，吃起来又没有丝毫的焦味，<strong>甜度比例得恰到好处，吃起来感觉刚刚好。</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>酥皮一口脆</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20200818/952c4aa8914d4d829ffb249809cd9cff.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20200818/7e054c36745f49d59aa8b4b774c006a8.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">酥皮层次感很分明，<strong>每咬一口基本上都会掉酥皮，</strong>香滑的蛋奶在口腔里很是满足，就是一定要趁热吃哦~</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>。冰火菠萝油</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20200818/8c5f5852d7524fbcaa2768d9bf670e02.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">诱惑力max的冰火菠萝包，<strong>菠萝包里加上一片香浓的黄油片</strong>，人间真香美味就是它了！拥有它，你就能收获N倍快乐~</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20200818/1e9117c5e2414d7c82c209ad41575a95.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20200818/843fde3ab5a44d4eacfe2f7802ed4a82.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/images01/20200818/70a7ba7901d545109d007cbc1ed61061.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20200818/bc66f720680f4e8ca6b5042fdfc49be7.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">菠萝包加上厚厚的两大块冰黄油，<strong>给你冰火两重天的口感！</strong>金黄的表皮一碰就掉渣，入口还有浓郁的咸香味，“老板，赶紧给我来十个”</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>。酥肉&amp;柠檬红茶</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20200818/79ea54f8675e40208f73750c5b5a2622.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20200818/2986b2031e744cb3b292f1bb3e8a7c88.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>听说饮品和小吃，与猪唛更配哦～</strong>一口<strong>清爽柠檬茶</strong>，一口猪扒包，再吃口<strong>焦脆酥肉</strong>，这份下午茶的搭配，令人一口入魂！</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20200818/efc9057e173c405c8a57c63a6d086c45.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">▩ 得闲一起“饮啖茶，食猪扒包”！ ▩</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20200818/ee9f4653475244d69fecd3f404219716.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20200818/8ac8fddacfa545508abecfad6c71f848.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>首秀旗下新式新餐饮品牌——猪唛PIGBAO，8月25日正式开业</strong>，快约上好友吃上一个能量满满的猪扒包，给自己的精神和身体同时补充能量8~</p>
